                                   <p style="color: orangered">Never pay for any notarisation, certificate or assessment as part of any recruitment process. When in doubt, <a style="color: orangered" href="/contact">contact us</a></p>
                MÃ©decins sans frontiÃ¨res (MSF) or Doctors Without Borders, is an international humanitarian-aid non-governmental organization (NGO) and Nobel Peace Prize laureate, best known for its projects in war-torn regions and developing countries facing endemic diseases.  

        <br />
    <a href="/jobs-at/medecins-sans-frontieres-msf" class="view-all2" style="margin-top:0px">Read more about this company</a>
        <p style="margin-bottom:0px;">&nbsp;</p>

        
